<cu-custom bgColor="bg-cyan" isBack="{{true}}">
	<view slot="backText">返回</view>
	<view slot="content">个人简介</view>
</cu-custom>
<view class="padding">
	<view class="padding-xl radius shadow-warp bg-white margin-top">
		<view class="flex justify-center">
			<image class="cu-avatar xl round" src="../../images/head_photo.jpg"></image>
		</view>
		<view class="flex justify-center margin-top-sm">
			<text class="text-bold">陈琦</text>
		</view>
		<view class="flex justify-center margin-top-sm">
			<text>期望职位：</text>
			<text class="text-shadow text-orange">web程序员</text>
		</view>
		<view class="flex justify-center margin-top-sm">
			<text>男</text>
			<text class="margin-left-sm">27岁</text>
			<text class="margin-left-sm">4年工作经验</text>
		</view>
		<view class="flex justify-around margin-top-sm">
			<view bindtap="showQrcode">
				<text class="cuIcon-weixin text-xl text-blue"></text>
				<text class="margin-left-xs">添加微信</text>
			</view>
			<view bindtap="phoneCall">
				<text class="cuIcon-phone text-xl text-blue"></text>
				<text class="margin-left-xs">拨打电话</text>
			</view>
			<view bindtap="saveContact">
				<text class="cuIcon-addressbook text-xl text-blue"></text>
				<text class="margin-left-xs">保存通讯录</text>
			</view>
		</view>
	</view>
	<view class="padding-xl radius shadow-warp bg-white margin-top format">
		<view class="cuIcon-group_fill text-xl text-blue text-center"></view>
		<view class="edu margin-top text-center text-bold"></view>
		<view class="margin-top">
			<text class="cuIcon-time"></text>
			<text class="margin-left-sm">2018年毕业</text>
		</view>
		<view class="margin-top-sm">
			<text class="cuIcon-home"></text>
			<text class="margin-left-sm">长治学院</text>
		</view>
		<view class="margin-top-sm">
			<text class="cuIcon-attentionfavor"></text>
			<text class="margin-left-sm">计算机/网络工程</text>
		</view>
	</view>
	<view class="padding-xl radius shadow-warp bg-white margin-top">
		<view class="cuIcon-medalfill text-xl text-blue text-center"></view>
		<view class="medalfill margin-top text-center text-bold"></view>
		<view class="margin-top evaluate-cont">
			<text>百度邀约参加智能小程序优化分享</text>
		</view>
	</view>
	<view class="padding-xl radius shadow-warp bg-white margin-top last-panel">
		<view class="cuIcon-appreciatefill text-xl text-blue text-center"></view>
		<view class="evaluate margin-top text-center text-bold"></view>
		<view class="margin-top evaluate-cont">
			<text>工作认真负责，能很好完成领导交代的任务。 </text>
			<text>喜欢研究新技术，平时有时间就看视频，补不足。</text>
			<text>喜欢逛码云、gitHub找一些有意思的开源项目或者功能学习然后加到自己个人项目中，已有个人博客、个人简历等三个开源项目。</text>
		</view>
	</view>
</view>